headline: CrowdStrike Named the Overall Frost Radar™ Leader for SaaS Security Posture Management (SSPM) for the Second Consecutive Time
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, October 27, 2025--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced it has been named the overall Leader in the 2025 Frost Radar™ for SaaS Security Posture Management (SSPM) for the second consecutive time, ranked highest of all vendors in growth and innovation.
